title: Analysis: Under Xi Jinping, zero-Covid is accelerating China's surveillance state
description: As a new, deadly virus overtook the central city of Wuhan and spread throughout China in early 2020, the country's ruling Communist Party and its leader Xi Jinping were faced with a crisis on a scale not seen in decades.

title: Indonesia bans sale of all cough syrups after 99 child deaths
description: Indonesia has halted the sale of all syrup and liquid medicines following the deaths of nearly 100 children and an unexplained spike in cases of acute kidney injuries.

title: Chinese stocks tumble to multi-year lows in New York and Hong Kong amid party congress
description: Chinese stocks have hit multi-year lows in New York and Hong Kong amid growing concerns about China's rising Covid cases and economic outlook.

title: Eight killed as parcel bombs and gunfire rock Myanmar's biggest jail
description: Bombs inside parcels exploded at Myanmar's biggest jail on Wednesday prompting soldiers to return fire in a confrontation in which at least eight people were killed, state media and a witness said.

title: Twitterverse vigilance scares LVMH CEO into dumping his private plane
description: Billionaires are no match for the Twitterverse.
